.TH LOA-AUTHORS 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
authors \- Show all authors with counts and top genres/tags
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> authors
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Displays one row per distinct author currently stored in the library.
.TP
Shows how many books exist per author.
.TP
Also shows the top genres and top tags affiliated with each author.
.TP
Rows are sorted by number of books (descending), then author name.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> authors
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-find-author(1), loa-list(1), loa-stats(1)
